Package: RAStools
Type: Package
Title: Rare Allele Sharing Block Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Lei", "Huang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "lei.huang@example.com")
Author: Lei Huang
Maintainer: Lei Huang <lei.huang@example.com>
Description: Computes block-based rare allele sharing statistics from population
    allele frequency and EIGENSTRAT genotype inputs. The package supports
    optional custom population definitions, site filters, frequency ascertainment
    bins, and jackknife summarization of block-level results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
